<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>17</hymn_number>
<author>jrjs mʿwḍ, jrjs mʿwḍ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (frḥt qlby ywm mạ qạbltk
 ywm mạ qạbltk kạn ywm ʿyd)2
 (kẖlṣtny ryḥt ḍmyry
 gẖyrt qlby bqlb jdyd)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt ḥbyby ạ̹nt ḥyạty
 ạ̹nt nṣyby ạ̉ʿẓm nṣyb)2
 (ạ̉ḥbbtny yạ yswʿ wạ̉nạ kẖạṭy
 ḥbk ẓhr ly fy ạlṣlyb)2
 2- (smʿt ṣwtk bynạdyny
 fy ậyẗ mn ậyạt ạlạ̹njyl)2
 (wjdt fyhạ tʿzyạty
 wkạn ṣwtk wạḍḥ wjmyl)2
 3- (fy lḥẓẗ wạḥdẗ ạ̉tgẖyr ḥạly
 sẖʿrt ạ̹ny ạ̹nsạn jdyd)2
 (sʿạdẗ lm tkẖṭr ʿly̱ bạly
 frḥ lạ ynṭq bh wmjyd)2
 4- (ʿndk nʿm wḥyạẗ ạ̉bdyẗ
 ʿndk ynbwʿ yrwy ạlʿṭsẖạn)2
 (ạ̹rwyny mn nbʿk yạ fạdyã
 lky ạ̉kwn dwmaⁿạ frḥạn)2</lyrics>
<title>frḥt qlby</title>
</song>